  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为物流仓库系统画一个状态流转图，核心是库存水位监控模块。起点应该是IDLE空闲态，收到Kick-off信号后进入FETCH状态去拉取数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_StockLevel",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "Kick-off"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，FETCH完成后是直接进入解析吗？还有，解析结果如果无效的话该怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "FETCH到PARSE的转移条件是Complete。PARSE之后要分支：数据Valid的话走ARB_READ去仲裁读请求，Invalid的话要进ERROR状态，等软件清除后回到IDLE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "Valid",
        "Invalid",
        "Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，PARSE的分支我加上了。ARB_READ获得Grant授权后进入READ状态，读完之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "Grant"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "READ完成后也是Complete，然后进入ARB_WRITE仲裁写请求，同样Grant之后进入WRITE状态。写完之后要进入CHAIN状态做链式处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "Complete",
        "Grant"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "CHAIN状态有两个出口对吧？如果是Next就回到FETCH继续下一条，如果是Last就到COMPLETE结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE",
        "Next",
        "Last"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，COMPLETE之后发送IRQ中断回到IDLE。还有ERROR分支，用SW clear软件清除回到IDLE。这样整个闭环就完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "IDLE",
        "IRQ sent",
        "ERROR",
        "SW clear"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有状态和转移都画好了，从Logistics_StockLevel进入IDLE，经过FETCH-PARSE-ARB_READ-READ-ARB_WRITE-WRITE-CHAIN的完整链路，异常分支和完成分支都能正确回到IDLE。",
